Package: simmer.json
Type: Package
Title: Translates JSON into a simmer environment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bart", "Smeets", email = "bartsmeets86@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Define a simmer simulation problem using JSON syntax.
  This makes for easy sharing of simulation definitions and for easily digesting a
  simulation definition through an API.
